  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates patient response to a motivation evolution chart for a medical-nutrition
      intervention as a continuation of a previous study: adherence to an overweight and obesity
      treatment available at: https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25101227
    </textblock>
